nodes.text: Keith Swaden (June 18, 1949 – January 18, 2015) was an actor and stuntman. He played various roles in the original trilogy. In Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope, he played a Stormtrooper. He played as both a rebel Soldier on Hoth and a Snowtrooper in Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back. Lastly, he acted as a rebel soldier in Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi.
